#subtitle: Outside of electoral politics, the SPD runs a social world onto itself.

= Party Organizations

In addition to being a political party, the SPD is a social world onto itself, with a vast array of associated organizations which serve the social needs of their members from cradle to grave.

- @newspapers: Attempt to boost our [+ mediahealth : mediahealth +] media.
- @welfare: Organize fundraisers for our most troubled trade unions.
- @chapters: Fund our local chapters in an attempt to boost activity.
- @rb: Organize a recruitment drive to attract new members.
- @youth: We have the reputation of being a party for old men. Support DSU, our youth organization.
- @nothing: Do not increase funding for any of this.
- @easy_discard

